1. Applicability of this Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy applies to Miro‚Äôs online collaboration tools and platform, including the associated Miro mobile and desktop applications (collectively, the ‚Äú
Services
‚Äù), miro.com and other Miro websites (collectively, the ‚Äú
Websites
‚Äù) and other interactions (e.g. customer support, the Miro Community, etc.) you may have with Miro, including the processing of any messages, text, files, images, video or audio recordings, or other content submitted through our Services (collectively, ‚Äú
Customer Content
‚Äù). This Privacy Policy does not apply to any third-party applications or software that integrate with our Services (‚Äú
Third-Party Services
